<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/22(Sun.) 10 Ways To Have a Better Conversation / How is Your Phone Changing You? (Host: Jennie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=619&amp;p=642#p642"><![CDATA[
5/22(Sun.) 10 Ways To Have a Better Conversation / How is Your Phone Changing You? (Host: Jennie)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br />Session 1: 10 Ways To Have a Better Conversation<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/R1vskiVDwl4">https://youtu.be/R1vskiVDwl4</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.What do you think that a good conversation requires?<br /><br />2.In conversation, do you agree with that we have something to learn?<br /><br />3.Which of the 10 rules do you think the most important one? Why?<br /><br />4.Which of the 10 rules do you struggle with the most? Why? <br /><br />------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session 2: How is Your Phone Changing You?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/W6CBb3yX9Zs">https://youtu.be/W6CBb3yX9Zs</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.In addition to phone callings and text messages, what functions else do you    utilize with your cell phone? Roughly how many hours do you use a day?<br /><br />2.Are there any problems with your body and brain caused by using cell      phone? Such as myopia, cervical spine, etc..<br /><br />3.Has the phenomenon of “ No Mobile Phobia “ happened to you? When you couldn’t find it or leave it home?<br /><br />4.On the other hand. what advantages have impacted to your life style by      using cell (smart) phone?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Thu May 19, 2022 2:39 pm</p><hr />
